quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,187,"Unibuke (yewe Muhamadi) ubwo Allah yahaga isezerano rikomeye abahawe igitabo (cya Tawurati n’Ivanjili) ry’uko bagomba kubisobanurira abantu batabihisha, ariko babiteye umugongo babigurana ikiguzi gito. Nyamara ibyo bahisemo ni bibi"
  3,188,"Ntukibwire ko ba bandi bishimira ibikorwa (bibi) bakoze, bakanakunda gushimirwa ibyo batakoze; rwose ntutekereze ko bazakiranuka n’ibihano; ahubwo bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza"
  3,189,"Kandi ubwami bw’ibirere n’ubw’isi ni ubwa Allah, ndetse Allah ni Ushobora byose"
  3,190,"Mu by’ukuri, mu kuremwa kw’ibirere n’isi no gusimburana kw’ijoro n’amanywa, harimo ibimenyetso ku banyabwenge"
  3,191,"Ba bandi basingiza Allah, baba bahagaze, bicaye, cyangwa baryamye, bakanatekereza ku iremwa ry’ibirere n’isi (bagira bati) “Nyagasani wacu! Ibi ntiwabiremye nta mpamvu. Ubutagatifu ni ubwawe! Ngaho turinde ibihano by’umuriro.”"
  3,192,"Nyagasani wacu! Mu by’ukuri, uwo uzinjiza mu muriro uzaba umusuzuguje; kandi inkozi z’ibibi ntizizigera zibona abatabazi"
  3,193,"Nyagasani wacu! Mu by’ukuri, twumvise umuhamagazi (Intumwa Muhamadi) uhamagarira ukwemera (agira ati) “Nimwemere Nyagasani wanyu”, nuko turemera. None Nyagasani wacu! Tubabarire ibyaha byacu, udukize ibicumuro byacu, kandi uzadukure ku isi turi mu beza"
  3,194,"Nyagasani wacu! Unaduhe ibyo wadusezeranyije binyuze ku ntumwa zawe. Kandi ntuzadukoze isoni ku munsi w’imperuka, kuko mu by’ukuri utajya wica isezerano (ryawe)"